{"tid":180828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本立例規管JK業務　禁未成年少女賣淫","createTime":"2017-03-31T07:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T00:03:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26857cdf8d7c9dc0436d4cb88bc4ec733c3e57e5","tid":180828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"2017年03月31日(五) 14:51<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170331/photo/bknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170331152404\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170331%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170331152404&h=a61a0327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當局為JK業務實施新例，以防止未成年女高中生提供性服務。（互聯網圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n專為男客人提供伴賞服務的東京新興女性行業「JK Business」（JK業務），當中涉及提供性服務的性質。為防止有日本高中生被捲入兒童賣淫等相關罪案，東京都議會於周四例行會議中，一致通過為該業務實施登記制，以禁止未滿18歲人士從事相關行業。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170331/photo/bknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001_02p.jpg?20170331152404\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170331%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20170331152404&h=fe04aa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">JK業務主要向男人客人提供陪賞服務，惟營業者不干預員工賣淫。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n</span><br />\n針對JK業務而首次立法規管的新例當中，JK業務性質將被定義為「特定異性接客營業」，並分為5種類別，包括為男客人提供陪睡、按摩、陪同散步或導遊服務等；至於營運JK業務的新公司，必須在東京都公安委員會登記，並需輯錄列明員工年齡及個人資料的名冊，必要時讓警方作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n有關規例將於7月1日起生效，違例單位可被當局下令停業，或對經營者及其員工判以少於1年徒刑，或罰款100萬日圓（約7.1萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170331/bknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170331%2Fbknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001.html&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=ebf3d703\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170331/bknint-20170331145146781-0331_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c8e455bba656242ef21517c20d75b51c1a62331","tid":180828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee6fc207fb24fc78649d8a4b3a41e177043c298","tid":180828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad15260add3c73b189a28ca8e8529033b672cf73","tid":180828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}